Vcs-Git: https://github.com/grml/tuitest.git
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/grml/tuitest

Package: tuitest
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: tool to create and run automated tests of text user interfaces
 tuitest is meant as a complement to the widespread use of unit tests, and uses
 concepts known from GUI testing tools with the difference that it applies
 them specifically to text- and terminal-based user interfaces.
